{"tid":665370,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"空姐搭滴滴車遭性侵身亡　影片曝光","createTime":"2018-05-15T01:39:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T14:31:24.000Z","uid":72009,"like":40,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":65,"replies":[{"pid":"aa119c6954db41d8ee239d391a0566f1058f8281","tid":665370,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:39:42.000Z","msg":"警方指，李明珠是在本月5日晚間11時52分上車，10分鐘後就因為被劉振華性騷擾，而透過微信向朋友抱怨：「遇到一個變態，說我長得特別美，特別想親我一口，幸虧沒坐前面」。而劉振華似乎打定主意，要硬上李明珠，在6日凌晨零時03分退出「滴滴打車」App，並註銷帳號。<br />\n負責本案的民警說，劉振華沒有依李明珠要求，前往鄭州火車站，而是從南向北行駛數分鐘後，來到一處荒地，在那停留約7分鐘，然後再調頭往相反方向行駛，「我們推斷在這7分鐘的時候，有可能在這個地方他把被害人進行了控制」。而後劉振華也被道路監視器拍到，他已赤裸上半身開車。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1353905\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1353905&d=kJqg1kpVOanmZM9Z9Y77dgCO%2BKh2Nr2cOOQ8tL9eopA%3D&h=06d7c694\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Frecommend%2Frealtime%2F20180515%2F1353905&h=bf703e9f\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/recommend/realtime/20180515/1353905</a><br />\n片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e872d986e5215820f74eb8cab570ca12858aeeab","tid":665370,"uid":66943,"like":3,"dislike":53,"score":-50,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:40:24.000Z","msg":"空姐搭滴滴車遭性侵<del>身亡</del>　影片曝光"},{"pid":"e511c0e003250623010ff0b5d210d1c5259ace9f","tid":665370,"uid":41737,"like":224,"dislike":0,"score":224,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:43:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e654b31fa8cbb78f1a6da59ad1c15e53e3ef3f11","tid":665370,"uid":20658,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-15T01:50:27.000Z","msg":"又一條on9"},{"pid":"64a2da1cfd5a8a27c320f543cf1edc37aa2395ee","tid":665370,"uid":14766,"like":128,"dislike":0,"score":128,"quote":{"pid":"e511c0e003250623010ff0b5d210d1c5259ace9f","tid":665370,"uid":41737,"like":224,"dislike":0,"score":224,"citedBy":2,"r